         BTW, the pet is not going to hit him if you mez the guy, so you are kinda screwed there.</P><P>Just keep it ready and only cast when he starts casting a spell.  When it lands you will get a message from pet that he can't wake him up.  Keep mashing /pet attack button cause ST will wear off when the DoTs hit him again (6 seconds or less) and Goober will be back on him like a bad habbit.</P><P>One other note.  I thought I read that this drops off all (or most) of the mobs in this room.  Can't remember where I read that.</P><P>-DV</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
