         Went down to ol Splitpaw tonight to get the last crystal for the Phenocryst's Focus quest (the crystal spawns a few feet from where the secret entrance to the Ishiva), so I decided to go for a free robe. So, I pull out a lvl 49 pet, buffed him with aug, then sent him into the fight. Cast Ebolt, Casc darkness, and then waited, got add and pet died (from the two guards). Second time up I realized I needed Manaskin. Buffed manaskin got out another 49 pet and buffed him, took down the two guards NP. Then I Screaming Terrored the guard inside the ishiva room, soon after the Ishiva came running WITH the guard. Casted Casc on Ishiva, Ebolt, then STed the guard. Got 3 or so nukes on me with heatblood. Ishiva got dotted down to 0.000001 HP when casc and ebolt wore :( (with extended affliction 3 bracer) waited till they moved on and gated the hell outta there.</P><P>Moral of the story: Uhh, I'm an idiot?</P><P>55 necro Tholuxe Paells</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
