         I went back last night and got my spell but needed a partner.  I figured I'd post this in case anyone does a search for the Ishva Mal.</P><P>I went in with a lvl 50 mage.  We invised and went through Splitpaw until we were outside of the Ishva Mal's room.  I was able to single pull the guards guarding the room and our pets demolished them.  Wasn't even fair.  Then I pulled the guard from inside the room along witht he ph and our pets destroyed them as well, very easy.  Then we just waited around for the Ishva Mal to pop and killed it, it dropped the summon corpse spell, the brains and a fine steel staff.</P><P>The point is that with 2 people is becomes very easy but with one necro before lvl 49 it is very difficult if not impossible.  You would have to be really lucky to single pull inside the Ishva Mal's room, but if you could do it then I think a necro under 49 could handle this.</P><P>Insert witty comment and original artwork here.</P><P>Corto Muerte<BR>45 Gnecromancer<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
